      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MR. UNFLAPPABLE (5) filled a minor placing last start at Capalaba behind Zipping Urban (20.02) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Key chance in this line up. OUT OF AUSTRIA (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing eighth (20.68) in a Grade 5 at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. SPRING MISTY (7) was in the minors two back (22.03) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 8th. Has a good record here at this journey. Expected to run well. FUTURE ETHICS (2) must be included in calculations.",
